Car keys.

00:15:48.080 --> 00:15:49.160
I'll buy you a meal when I get back.

00:15:49.160 --> 00:15:49.800
Remember

00:15:49.800 --> 00:15:50.530
to fix my car.

00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:51.240
Don't worry.

00:15:51.240 --> 00:15:52.100
I'll go in a bit.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:58.240
Brother.

00:15:58.880 --> 00:16:00.200
My dad agreed.

00:16:57.040 --> 00:16:57.800
Master.

00:16:59.200 --> 00:17:00.000
Calm down.

00:17:00.760 --> 00:17:02.120
Master.

00:17:10.119 --> 00:17:13.200
I've lived aimlessly for over ten years.

00:17:14.520 --> 00:17:16.980
Finally, I had something to look forward to.

00:17:18.720 --> 00:17:20.240
In an instant...

00:17:20.800 --> 00:17:22.960
It's all gone.

00:17:33.680 --> 00:17:34.280
Guannan.

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:39.200
I'll help you.

00:17:39.320 --> 00:17:39.760
Go.

00:17:56.240 --> 00:17:57.970
About what happened back then,

00:17:58.040 --> 00:17:59.600
he was the one hit hardest.

00:18:00.560 --> 00:18:02.090
He doesn't really hate you.

00:18:02.200 --> 00:18:04.520
He just can't vent his pain and anger.

00:18:06.480 --> 00:18:07.600
Give him some time.

00:18:16.200 --> 00:18:16.960
You too.

00:18:17.880 --> 00:18:19.400
Even if you want to find the real killer,

00:18:19.400 --> 00:18:20.880
you have to move on first.